        "content": "<p>I think the missing result is something like <code>Pairwise R ↔(∀ x. R 0 (succ x)) ∧ (∀ x. R (succ x) 0) ∧ Pairwise (fun x y =&gt; R (succ x) (succ y))</code></p>",
